h1 Dear Shopping Cart,
p We are pleased to inform you that a new order has been placed at your store.
strong Customer Information:
ul
  li 
    | Customer's Name: 
    = @user.last_name
  li
    | Shipping Address: 
    = @order.address
  li
    | Contact Number: 
    = @order.phone 
Strong Order Information:
- @order.order_items.each do |item|
  ul
    li
      strong 
        | Product:  
        = item.name
    li
      | Quantity:  
      = item.quantity
    li
      | Price: 
      = item.price
    li
      | Subtotal:  
      = item.quantity * item.price
strong
  | Total price: 
  = @order.total_price
